0and%20%26quot%3Bproud%20Indians%26quot%3B%20with%20significant%20contributions%20to%20the%20sport.%20He%20believes%20Kohli%20should%20not%20have%20said%20such%20a%20thing.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fipl%2Ftop-stories%2Fvirat-shouldnt-have-said-it-wasim-akram-on-virat-kohli-sunil-gavaskar-spat-in-ipl%2Farticleshow%2F109915066.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BPeople%20Will%20Lose%20Faith%26quot%3B%3A%20Chief%20Justice's%20Big%20Remark%20In%20Bengal%20Jobs%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20Supreme%20Court%20bench%20led%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20put%20tough%20questions%20to%20the%20West%20Bengal%20government%20today%20while%20hearing%20its%20appeal%20against%20a%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20order%20to%20cancel%20about%2025%2C000%20appointments%20by%20the%20state%20school%20service%20commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20outset%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20asked%20the%20Bengal%20government%20why%20it%20created%20supernumerary%20posts%20and%20hired%20waitlisted%20candidates%20when%20the%20selection%20process%20itself%20had%20been%20challenged%20in%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20the%20court%20through%20the%20high%20court%20order%2C%20the%20Bengal%20government's%20counsel%2C%20Senior%20Advocate%20Neeraj%20Kishan%20Kaul%20asked%20if%20such%20an%20order%20can%20be%20sustained.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20even%20CBI's%20case%20that%2025%2C000%20appointments%20are%20all%20illegal.%20Everything%2C%20teacher-child%20ratio%20is%20gone%20for%20a%20toss%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20Advocate%20Jaideep%20Gupta%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20school%20service%20commission%2C%20argued%20that%20the%20high%20court%20bench%20did%20not%20have%20the%20jurisdiction%20to%20cancel%20the%20jobs%20and%20its%20orders%20were%20in%20conflict%20with%20Supreme%20Court%20judgments%20in%20the%20matter.%20When%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20asked%20if%20OMR%20sheets%20and%20scanned%20copies%20of%20answer%20sheets%20had%20been%20destroyed%2C%20he%20replied%20in%20the%20affirmative.%20The%20Chief%20Justice%20then%20asked%20why%20a%20tender%20was%20not%20issued%20for%20%26quot%3Bsuch%20a%20sensitive%20matter%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Justice%20then%20asked%20it%20was%20the%20commission's%20duty%20to%20keep%20digital%20copies%20of%20these%20sheets.%20When%20Mr%20Gupta%20responded%20that%20it%20is%20with%20the%20agency%20that%20the%20work%20was%20outsourced%20to%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BWhere%3F%20CBI%20did%20not%20find%20it.%20It%20is%20outsourced%2C%20not%20with%20you.%20Can%20there%20be%20a%20greater%20breach%20of%20security%20protocols%3F%20They%20were%20only%20hired%20for%20scanning%2C%20but%20you%20let%20them%20have%20the%20entire%20data.%20You%20cannot%20say%20they%20took%20it%20away%2C%20you%20are%20responsible%20for%20maintaining%20people's%20data.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Justice%20then%20asked%20if%20the%20commission%20had%20wrongly%20told%20RTI%20applicants%20that%20it%20had%20the%20data.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20data%20(with%20you)%20at%20all.%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gupta%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BThat%20may%20be.%26quot%3B%20When%20he%20asked%20if%20the%20high%20court's%20directions%20were%20fair%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BBut%20this%20is%20systemic%20fraud.%20Public%20jobs%20are%20extremely%20scarce%20today%20and%20are%20looked%20at%20for%20social%20mobility.%20What%20remains%20in%20the%20system%20if%20their%20appointments%20are%20also%20maligned%3F%20People%20will%20lose%20faith%2C%20how%20do%20you%20countenance%20this%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%20appearing%20for%20the%20commission%2C%20Senior%20Advocate%20Sanjay%20Hegde%20said%20there%20is%20nothing%20in%20the%20high%20court%20judgment%20about%20irregularities%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20commission.%20%26quot%3BIf%20we%20lose%20a%20whole%20chunk%20or%20generation%20in%20between%2C%20we%20will%20lose%20senior%20headmasters%20and%20examiners%20for%20the%20future.%20Lordships%20may%20bear%20in%20mind%20that%20many%20of%20them%20did%20not%20get%20any%20notice.%20When%20there%20is%20a%20headache%2C%20you%20do%20not%20cut%20off%20your%20entire%20head%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20counsels%20also%20pointed%20out%20some%20candidates%20are%20completely%20untainted%20and%20their%20OMR%20sheets%20are%20seen%20as%20correct.%20A%20segregation%20between%20tainted%20and%20untainted%20candidates%2C%20they%20contended%2C%20was%20placed%20before%20the%20high%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20last%20week%20paused%20the%20high%20court%20order%20asking%20the%20CBI%20to%20investigate%20Bengal%20government%20officials%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20teacher%20recruitment%20scam.%20It%20had%20refused%20to%20stay%20the%20cancellation%20of%20the%20appointment%20of%20over%2025%2C000%20teaching%20and%20non-teaching%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20had%20also%20asked%20if%20it%20was%20possible%20to%20segregate%20the%20valid%20and%20invalid%20appointments%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20material%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20government%20has%20argued%20that%20the%20high%20court%20has%20cancelled%20the%20appointments%20%26quot%3Barbitrarily%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20high%20court%20failed%20to%20appreciate%20the%20ramification%20of%20cancelling%20the%20entire%20selection%20process%2C%20leading%20to%20straightaway%20termination%20of%20teaching%20and%20non-teaching%20staff%20from%20service%20with%20immediate%20effect%2C%20without%20giving%20sufficient%20time%20to%20the%20petitioner%20state%20to%20deal%20with%20such%20an%20exigency%2C%20rendering%20the%20education%20system%20at%20a%20standstill%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20petition%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20has%20said%20in%20its%20April%2022%20order%20that%20the%20appointments%20are%20violative%20of%20Articles%2014%20and%2016%20of%20the%20Constitution.%20The%20court%20had%20observed%20that%20it%20had%20given%20%26quot%3Banxious%20consideration%20to%20the%20passionate%20plea%26quot%3B%20that%20persons%20who%20obtained%20the%20appointments%20legally%20would%20be%20prejudiced%20if%20the%20entire%20selection%20process%20was%20cancelled%2C%20but%20added%20that%20it%20hardly%20had%20any%20choice%20left.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20282-page%20judgment%2C%20the%20court%20had%20said%20retaining%20appointees%20selected%20through%20%26quot%3Bsuch%20a%20dubious%20process%26quot%3B%20would%20be%20contrary%20to%20public%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715075040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fuqrqrqg8_justice-dy-chandrachud-ani-_625x300_03_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbengal-teachers-recruitment-case-cji-dy-chandrachud-people-will-lose-faith-chief-justices-big-remark-in-bengal-jobs-case-5607902%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Supreme%20Court%20bench%20led%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20put%20tough%20questions%20to%20the%20West%20Bengal%20government%20today%20while%20hearing%20its%20appeal%20against%20a%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20order%20to%20cancel%20about%2025%2C000%20appointments%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbengal-teachers-recruitment-case-cji-dy-chandrachud-people-will-lose-faith-chief-justices-big-remark-in-bengal-jobs-case-5607902%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbengal-teachers-recruitment-case-cji-dy-chandrachud-people-will-lose-faith-chief-justices-big-remark-in-bengal-jobs-case-5607902%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F