aring%20for%20IMA%2C%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20were%20praising%20(the)%20court%20for%20(the)%20most%20part...%20but%20then%20he%20(Asokan)%20fell%20into%20a%20leading%20question%2C%20he%20just%20fell%20into%20it.%26quot%3B%20The%20court%20said%20it%20had%20raised%20the%20matter%20last%20week%20and%20had%20expected%20the%20IMA%20to%20respond.%20When%20the%20doctors'%20body%20said%20it%20didn't%20want%20to%20pre-empt%20anything%2C%20the%20bench%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20were%20you%20pre-empting%3F%20Your%20client%20-%20no%20less%20than%20the%20President%20(of%20IMA)%20goes%20to%20the%20press%20on%20a%20matter%20that%20is%20subjudice.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20noted%20that%20the%20IMA%20counsel's%20%26quot%3Binnocent%20reply%20is%20not%20persuading%20us%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BSee%20what%20damage%20he%20has%20caused%20to%20himself!%20Now%20let%20us%20see%2C%20we%20gave%20you%20an%20opportunity%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Amanullah%20said.%20%26quot%3BLet%20us%20make%20it%20clear%2C%20this%20court%20is%20not%20expecting%20any%20pats%20on%20the%20back.%20This%20court%20has%20also%20received%20its%20share%20of%20brickbats.%20We%20also%20have%20broad%20shoulders%20but...%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Kohli%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Patwalia%20requested%20for%20time%20till%20the%20next%20date%20of%20hearing.%20%26quot%3BHe%20(IMA%20president)%20is%20feeling%20sorry%2C%20he%20realises%20he%20should%20have%20just%20kept%20his%20mouth%20shut%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20court.%20The%20court%20was%20firm.%20%26quot%3BSee%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20matter%20was%20proceeding.%20The%20views%20of%20the%20court%20equally%20apply%20to%20you.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBalkrishna%2C%20managing%20director%20of%20Patanjali%20Ayurved%2C%20had%20approached%20the%20court%20over%20the%20IMA%20president's%20interview%20to%20PTI%2C%20contending%20that%20his%20statements%20are%20a%20direct%20interference%20in%20the%20court's%20proceedings.%20%26quot%3BThese%20statements%20are%20condemnable%20in%20nature%20and%20a%20clear%20attempt%20to%20lower%20the%20dignity%20of%20this%20Honorable%20Court%20and%20the%20majesty%20of%20law%20in%20the%20eyes%20of%20the%20public%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20petition%20said%2C%20seeking%20action%20against%20the%20IMA%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20developments%20were%20a%20reversal%20of%20sorts%20after%20the%20court's%20strong%20rebuke%20of%20Ramdev%20and%20Balkrishna%20for%20misleading%20ads%20that%20claimed%20Patanjali%20products%20could%20cure%20health%20conditions%20such%20as%20high%20blood%20pressure%20and%20diabetes.%20The%20court%20rejected%20multiple%20sets%20of%20apologies%20by%20the%20two%2C%20pointing%20to%20their%20statements%20in%20the%20media.%20Ramdev%20and%20Balkrishna%20subsequently%20put%20out%20prominent%20apologies%20in%20newspapers%20as%20per%20the%20court's%20orders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20petition%20against%20the%20yoga%20guru%20and%20his%20Haridwar-based%20firm%2C%20the%20IMA%20had%20earlier%20flagged%20its%20advertisements%20that%20allegedly%20projected%20the%20allopathy%20and%20the%20doctors%20in%20poor%20light.%20The%20doctors'%20body%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Bcontinuous%2C%20systematic%2C%20and%20unabated%20spread%20of%20misinformation%26quot%3B%20comes%20alongside%20Patanjali's%20efforts%20to%20make%20false%20claims%20about%20curing%20certain%20diseases%20through%20the%20use%20of%20Patanjali%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715074020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F9n5s1f2o_ramdev-balkrishna_625x300_07_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Framdev-patanjali-ads-case-tables-turn-court-grills-doctors-body-after-patanjali-flags-interview-5608542%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20stunning%20change%20of%20fortune%2C%20the%20Indian%20Medical%20Association%20(IMA)%20was%20at%20the%20receiving%20end%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20retort%20during%20today's%20hearing%20in%20th