%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fworld-news%2Fsaudi-aramco-maintains-31-bn-dividend-despite-lower-net-income-in-q1-124050700686_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fworld-news%2Fsaudi-aramco-maintains-31-bn-dividend-despite-lower-net-income-in-q1-124050700686_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BDepriving%20Right%20To%20Life%26quot%3B%3A%20Top%20Court%20During%20Hearing%20On%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20Plea%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EInvestigating%20agencies%20cannot%20%26quot%3Bselectively%20pick%26quot%3B%20between%20material%20that%20speaks%20to%20an%20individual's%20innocence%20and%20that%20which%20may%20confirm%20guilt%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20noted%20Tuesday%20as%20it%20heard%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20plea%20challenging%20his%20arrest%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20in%20the%20alleged%20liquor%20policy%20scam.%20The%20court%20asked%20the%20central%20agency%20-%20which%20had%20arrested%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20on%20March%2021%20-%20%26quot%3BIf%20there%20is%20evidence%20that%20points%20towards%20guilt...%20and%20other%20that%20points%20towards%20innocence...%20can%20you%20selectively%20pick%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIs%20this%20an%20administrative%20task%3F%20You%20need%20to%20strike%20a%20balance%20between%20the%20two.%20You%20cannot%20exclude%20one%20aspect.%20You%20are%20depriving%20a%20person%20of%20their%20right%20to%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Dipankar%20Datta%2C%20part%20of%20a%20two-judge%20bench%20that%20includes%20Justice%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%2C%20said%20firmly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20this%20Additional%20Solicitor%20General%20SV%20Raju%20-%20appearing%20for%20the%20ED%20-%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20agency's%20remit%2C%20at%20this%20time%2C%20was%20only%20to%20supply%20%26quot%3Breasons%20to%20believe%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20individual's%20guilt.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMaterial%20must%20show%20person%20is%20guilty%20of%20offense...%20that%20is%20only%20material%20to%20be%20reflected%20in%20'reasons%20to%20believe'...%20that%20is%20what%20Section%2019%20(of%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act)%20contemplates.%20It%20isn't%20necessary%20for%20me%20to%20say%20in%20'reasons%20to%20believe'%20I%20have%20considered%20all%20material%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20in%20a%20potentially%20key%20moment%20today%2C%20the%20court%20also%20asked%20Mr%20Raju%20why%20it%20had%20taken%20the%20central%20agency%20two%20years%20to%20act%20against%20the%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%20executive%26quot%3B%20-%20referring%20to%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20his%20party.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...issue%20is%20that%20it%20has%20taken%20two%20years%20for%20this.%20It%20is%20not%20good%20for%20any%20investigating%20agency%20to%20say%20that%20it%20takes%20two%20years%20to%20unearth...%20now%20when%20will%20the%20trial%20start%3F%20From%20one%20stage%20to%20the%20other...%20from%20initiation%20of%20proceedings%20to%20arrest...%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20asked%20the%20ED.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20asked%20the%20ED%20why%20it%20was%20that%20%26quot%3Bno%20question%20was%20asked%20about%20him%20(Mr%20Kejriwal)%26quot%3B%2C%20prior%20to%20summons%20being%20issued%20and%20his%20arrest%2C%20during%20the%20course%20of%20its%20investigation.%20%26quot%3B...%20only%20issue%20is%20why%20did%20you%20not%20ask%20and%20why%20you%20were%20delaying%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20start%20asking%20about%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20at%20the%20outset...%20it%20would%20have%20been%20called%20'malafide'...%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Raju%20responded%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20takes%20time%20to%20understand...%20we%20can't%20put%20it%20overnight.%20Things%20have%20to%20be%20confirmed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20Mr%20Raju%20had%20recounted%20statements%20of%20approvers%20-%20i.e.%2C%20ex-acc