0a%20million%20views.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20continually%20restrict%20the%20freedom%20of%20marriage%20as%20a%20legitimate%20social%20option%2C%20when%20we%20do%20this%20to%20people%20who%20are%20of%20a%20ripe%2C%20fertile%20age%20and%20may%20have%20a%20pregnancy%20and%20a%20baby%20involved%2C%20are%20we%20not%20in%20fact%20making%20abortion%20a%20much%20more%20desirable%20alternative%2C%20when%20marriage%20might%20be%20the%20right%20solution%20for%20some%20freedom-loving%20couples%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20is%20heard%20saying%20in%20the%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThis%20is%20New%20Hampshire%20Republican%20State%20Rep%20Jess%20Edwards%20arguing%20in%20favor%20of%20child%20marriage%20this%20week%20and%20referring%20to%20girls%20as%20%E2%80%9Cripe%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cfertile.%E2%80%9D%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThankfully%2C%20the%20bill%20passed%20and%20child%20marriage%20will%20soon%20be%20illegal%20in%20New%20Hampshire.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FRJSYL8rpVS%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FRJSYL8rpVS%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Shannon%20Watts%20(%40shannonrwatts)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fshannonrwatts%2Fstatus%2F1786751662935380205%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMay%204%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%20seeks%20to%20raise%20New%20Hampshire's%20minimum%20marriage%20age%20to%2018%2C%20which%20currently%20is%2016.%20Mr%20Edwards'%20remarks%20were%20met%20with%20laughter%20in%20the%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20his%20intervention%2C%20the%20legislature%20passed%20the%20bill%20and%20sent%20it%20to%20Governor%20Chris%20Sununu%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsweek.com%2Fjess-edwards-teen-child-marriage-opposed-republican-ripe-fertile-age-1897512%5C%22%3Eas%20per%20%3Cem%3ENewsweek%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENew%20Hampshire%20state%20representative%20Wendy%20Thomas%2C%20a%20democrat%2C%20was%20among%20those%20who%20criticised%20the%20lawmaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20what%20we%20are%20up%20against%20in%20New%20Hampshire.%20A%20grown%20old%20man%20on%20the%20N.H.%20house%20floor%20defending%20child%20marriage%20(no%20age%20limit%20at%20all)%20because%20those%20children%20(girls)%20are%20'ripe%20and%20fertile'%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Thomas%20wrote%20on%20her%20Facebook%20page.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Mr%20Edwards%20said%20by%20exploiting%20his%20poor%20word%20choice%2C%20some%20people%20are%20creating%20distraction%20from%20the%20fundamental%20issue%20-%20government%20restricting%20the%20freedoms%20of%2016%20and%2017-year-olds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20somebody's%20old%20enough%20to%20engage%20in%20sex%2C%20they're%20old%20enough%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20consequences%20of%20pregnancy.%20So%20I%20believe%20in%20having%20people%20be%20responsible%20and%20having%20the%20freedom%20of%20choice%20to%20meet%20their%20responsibilities%20the%20best%20way%20they%20can%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Edwards%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.masslive.com%2Fpolitics%2F2024%2F05%2Fnh-lawmaker-opposes-new-marriage-bill-says-teens-are-of-ripe-fertile-age.html%5C%22%3Etold%20%3Cem%3EMassLive%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20explained%20the%20reason%20behind%20choosing%20the%20words%20%26quot%3Bripe%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bfertile%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20anyone%20should%20be%20upset%20about%20the%20use%20of%20the%20word%20fertile%20because%20that's%20the%20foundation%20of%20pregnancy%20and%20that's%20the%20trigger%20for%20abortion.%20So%20for%20people%20to%20react%20to%20the%20word%20fertile%2C%20I%20just%20think%20it's%20ridiculous.%20It's%20an%20emotionally-laden%20driven%20issue%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20word%20%26quot%3Bripe%26qu