%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715057723000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F1555B%2Fproduction%2F_133278378_gettyimages-2151802970.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fentertainment-arts-68938637%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Zendaya%2C%20Sabrina%20Carpenter%20and%20Gigi%20Hadid%20were%20among%20the%20stars%20walking%20the%20red%20carpet%20in%20New%20York.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A578%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fentertainment-arts-68938637%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fentertainment-arts-68938637.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fentertainment-arts-68938637.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Research%20Body%20Asks%20Staff%20To%20Wear%20Wrinkled%20Clothes%20On%20Mondays.%20Here's%20Why%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETill%20now%2C%20one%20had%20heard%20of%20'Thank%20God%20It's%20Friday'%20or%20'Casual%20Friday'%20dress%20code%20followed%20by%20many%20corporates.%20As%20part%20of%20this%2C%20employees%20avoid%20formal%20clothes%20on%20Fridays%20and%20turn%20up%20to%20work%20in%20semiformal%20relaxed%20outfits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20the%20Council%20of%20Scientific%20and%20Industrial%20Research%20(CSIR)%2C%20the%20largest%20civilian%20network%20of%20research%20labs%20in%20India%2C%20has%20started%20a%20'WAH%20Mondays'%20campaign%20--%20WAH%20expanded%20to%20'Wrinkles%20Acche%20Hai'%20(wrinkles%20are%20good).%20The%20idea%20is%20to%20get%20people%20to%20wear%20non-ironed%20clothes%20to%20work%20every%20Monday%20in%20a%20symbolic%20fight%20against%20climate%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20N%20Kalaiselvi%2C%20secretary%20of%20Department%20of%20Scientific%20and%20Industrial%20Research%20and%20the%20first%20woman%20director%20general%20of%20CSIR%2C%20says%20WAH%20Mondays%20is%20part%20of%20a%20larger%20energy%20literacy%20campaign.%20%26quot%3BCSIR%20decided%20to%20contribute%20by%20wearing%20non-ironed%20clothes%20on%20Mondays.%20Ironing%20each%20set%20of%20clothes%20amounts%20to%20emission%20of%20200%20g%20of%20carbon%20dioxide.%20So%2C%20by%20wearing%20non-ironed%20clothes%2C%20one%20can%20prevent%20emission%20of%20carbon%20dioxide%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20200%20g%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20'Wrinkles%20Acche%20Hain'%20campaign%20has%20been%20launched%20as%20part%20of%20the%20'Swachhata%20Pakhwada'%20from%20May%201-15.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20its%20larger%20initiative%20to%20save%20energy%2C%20CSIR%20is%20implementing%20a%20few%20standard%20operating%20procedures%20to%20reduce%20electricity%20consumption%20in%20all%20labs%20across%20the%20country%2C%20with%20an%20initial%20target%20of%2010%20per%20cent%20reduction%20of%20electricity%20charges%20at%20workplace.%20These%20SOPs%20will%20be%20implemented%20during%20June-August%202024%20as%20a%20pilot%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20the%20country's%20biggest%20climate%20clock%20was%20installed%20in%20the%20CSIR%20headquarters%20building%20in%20Delhi's%20Rafi%20Marg.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20CSIR's%20contribution%20to%20save%20mother%20Earth%20and%20the%20planet%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Kalaiselvi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715057700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fmp1iscpo_wrinkled-clothes_625x300_07_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fresearch-body-csir-asks-staff-to-wear-wrinkled-clothes-on-mondays-heres-why-5606565%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Till%20now%2C%20one%20had%20heard%20of%20'Thank%20God%20It's%20Friday'%20or%20'Casual%20Friday'%20dress%20code%20followed%20by%20many%20corporates.%20As%20part%20of%20this%2C%20employees%20avoid%20formal%20clothes%20on%20Fridays%20and%20turn%20up%20to%20work%20in%20semiformal%20relaxed%20outfits.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%2