%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F348813%2Fhow-to-check-for-fake-or-real-paneer-cottage-cheese-simple-tests-tricks-to-do-at-home%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Doctor%20Uses%20Grandpa%E2%80%99s%20Secrets%20to%20Grow%20Fruits%20%26amp%3B%20Veggies%20on%20Terrace%3B%20Has%20Helped%205000%20People%20Learn%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPlaying%20with%20mud%2C%20splashing%20water%20on%20plants%2C%20and%20picking%20fresh%20produce%20from%20their%20terrace%20garden%20are%20some%20of%20the%20childhood%20memories%20that%20Dr%20Naveen%20Kumar%20treasures.%20Growing%20vegetables%20was%20merely%20a%20fun%20hobby%20for%20the%20Chennai%20resident%20until%202016%20when%20he%20became%20a%20physiotherapy%20doctor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20get%20several%20patients%20who%20complained%20of%20gastrointestinal%20issues.%20The%20underlying%20cause%20of%20such%20rising%20issues%20is%20the%20consumption%20of%20adulterated%20food%20that%20is%20prepared%20using%20genetically%20modified%20seeds%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Naveen%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20market%20is%20flooded%20with%20genetically%20modified%20seeds%20which%20negatively%20affect%20human%20health.%20There%20have%20been%20concerns%20that%20the%20food%20prepared%20using%20such%20seeds%20has%20carcinogenic%20properties%20and%20could%20lead%20to%20the%20development%20of%20cancer%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%202016%2C%20Dr%20Naveen%20was%20eager%20to%20encourage%20residents%20to%20take%20up%20organic%20farming%20at%20home.%20In%20the%20past%2010%20years%2C%20the%2029-year-old%20has%20transformed%20his%20350%20sq%20ft%20terrace%20into%20a%20green%20haven.%20Using%20his%20%3Cem%3Ethatha%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20(grandfather)%20best%20gardening%20secrets%2C%20he%20currently%20grows%20more%20than%20250%20varieties%20of%20fruits%20and%20vegetables%20%E2%80%94%20including%20spinach%2C%20tomatoes%2C%20brinjals%2C%20custard%20apple%2C%20lemons%2C%20mulberries%2C%20and%20dragon%20fruits%20in%20a%20small%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FChennai-dr-naveen-1-1714627454.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Using%20his%20grandpa's%20gardening%20secrets%2C%20Dr%20Naveen%20grows%20more%20than%20250%20varieties%20of%20fruits%20and%20vegetables.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FChennai-dr-naveen-1-1714627454.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FChennai-dr-naveen-1-1714627454-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FChennai-dr-naveen-1-1714627454-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FChennai-dr-naveen-1-1714627454-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FChennai-dr-naveen-1-1714627454-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-348778%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EUsing%20his%20grandpa%E2%80%99s%20gardening%20secrets%2C%20Dr%20Naveen%20grows%20more%20than%20250%20varieties%20of%20fruits%20and%20vegetables.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPrescription%20for%20a%20long%20healthy%20life%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20his%20childhood%2C%20Naveen%20grew%20up%20surrounded%20by%20vegetables%20and%20fruit%20trees%20that%20were%20nurtured%20using%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F346317%2Fassam-organic-farmer-neelam-dutta-conserves-climate-resilient-heirloom-seeds-pabhoi-greens-northeast%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enative%20seeds%3C%2Fa%3E.%20However%2C%20growing%20up%20he%20understood%20that%20these%20seeds%20were%20fast%20disappearing%20due%20to%20modernisation%20and%20hunger%20for%20harvesting%20more%20produce%20in%20less%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20we%20see%20only%20green-coloured%20ladyfingers%20in%20the%20market%20when%20there%20are%20several%20native%20variants%20including%20the%20red-coloured%20torpedo%20shaped%20variety%20and%20light%20green-coloured%20long%20elephant%20tusk%20variety%20that%20has%20more%20amount%20of%20amino%20acids%20and%20iron%20content.%20Similarly%2C%20we%20get%20only%20hybrid%20tomatoes%20even%20though%20we%20have%20more%20than%20200%20native%20tomato%20varieties%20with%20distinct%20tastes%20and%20nutritional%20content.%20Irrespective%20of%20their%20benefits%2C%20you%20won%E2%80%99t%20find%20those%20vegetables%20in%20markets%20at%20all%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20points%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20where%20have%20these%20vegetables%20disappeared%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUnfortunately%2C%20we%20are%20forced%20to%20eat%20only%20genetically%20modified%20hybrid%20varieties.%20Genetically%20modified%20seeds%20only%20respond%20to%20chemical%20insecticides%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Naveen%2C%20%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20we%20can%20reduce%20this%20dependency%20by%20growing%20our%20own%20vegetables.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20every%20two%20years%2C%20he%20travels%20to%20Kolli%20hills%20%E2%80%94%20roughly%20400%20km%20from%20his%20home%20%E2%80%94%20to%20collect%20native%20varieties%20of%20seeds%20from%20tribal%20people%20in%20the%20region.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20the%20seeds%20I%20source%20are%20in%20limited%20numbers%2C%20I%20use%20them%20to%20grow%20produce%20at%20home.%20After%20harvesting%2C%20I%20scoop%20out%20the%20seeds%20in%20large%20quantities%20and%20then%20distribute%20them%20to%20the%20community.%20Using%20native%20seeds%2C%20farmers%20and%20gardeners%20do%20not%20need%20to%20buy%20seeds%20for%20the%20next%20season%2C%20and%20using%20a%20similar%20approach%2C%20they%20pass%20on%20seeds%20to%20others%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThat%E2%80%99s%20our%20motto!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FChennai-dr-naveen-3-1714627698.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Naveen%20grew%20up%20surrounded%20by%20vegetables%20and%20fruit%20trees%20that%20were%20nurtured%20using%20native%20seeds.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FChennai-dr-naveen-3-1714627698.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FChennai-dr-naveen-3-1714627698-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FChennai-dr-naveen-3-1714627698-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FChennai-dr-naveen-3-1714627698-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FChennai-dr-naveen-3-1714627698-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-348780%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENaveen%20grew%20up%20surrounded%20by%20vegetables%20and%20fruit%20trees%20that%20were%20nurtured%20using%20native%20seeds.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20Dr%20Naveen%20along%20with%20a%20group%20of%20like-minded%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F347565%2Fgrow-mangoes-chikoo-fruits-on-trees-urban-gardener-jayanti-sahoo-terrace-gardening-tips%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eterrace%20gardeners%20%3C%2Fa%3Econduct%20offline%20workshops%20in%20Chennai%20to%20promote%20organic%20farming.%20So%20far%2C%20he%20has%20reached%20out%20to%20more%20than%205%2C000%20people%20across%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20helped%20them%20cultivate%20vegetables%20and%20fruits%20at%20home.%20Besides%2C%20he%20also%20gives%20these%20native%20seeds%20to%20his%20patients%20along%20with%20prescriptions%20to%20lead%20a%20healthier%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGrow%20your%20veggies%20with%20these%20five%20secret%20techniques%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Naveen%20encourages%20everyone%20to%20embark%20on%20their%20organic%20farming%20journey%20%E2%80%94%20starting%20right%20at%20home%20with%20basic%20vegetables%20like%20tomatoes%2C%20lady%E2%80%99s%20fingers%2C%20and%20leafy%20greens%20such%20as%20spinach.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDrawing%20from%20the%20cherished%20teachings%20handed%20down%20by%20his%20grandfather%2C%20he%20shares%20a%20handful%20of%20techniques%20for%20cultivating%20vegetables%20and%20fruits%20effortlessly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20prepare%20a%20potting%20mix%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Naveen%20suggests%20taking%20soil%2C%20cocopeat%2C%20and%20vermicompost%20in%20a%20ratio%20of%201%3A2%3A2.%20After%20mixing%20them%2C%20keep%20the%20potting%20mix%20in%20a%20pot%20or%20container%20for%20three%20to%20four%20days.%20Sprinkle%20water%20once%20every%20morning%20and%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20will%20enhance%20microbial%20activities%20in%20the%20soil.%20You%20can%20sow%20seeds%20thereafter%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FChennai-dr-naveen-2-1714627600.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Naveen%20grows%20native%20vegetables%20like%20spinach%2C%20tomatoes%2C%20brinjals%2C%20and%20okra%20in%20a%20small%20space.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fupload