s%20as%20he%20would%20get%20if%20he%20were%20borrowing%20from%20a%20bank.%20He%20will%20get%20a%20credit%20score%20in%20all%20the%20four%20credit%20bureaus%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20clarifies%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20how%20the%20Matheran%20project%20strikes%20a%20chord%20in%20him%2C%20Ram%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20liberating%20to%20know%20that%20a%20practice%20(hand-pulled%20rickshaws)%20that%20has%20been%20in%20existence%20since%20the%20British%20era%20will%20be%20put%20to%20an%20end.%E2%80%9D%20He%20sees%20this%20as%20a%20classic%20textbook%20example%20of%20blending%20many%20social%20factors%20%E2%80%94%20engaging%20communities%2C%20protecting%20the%20environment%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F318643%2Fengineer-helps-mir-nomadic-community-gujarat-sell-traditional-beadwork-tokar-designs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecreating%20dignified%20livelihoods%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20into%20one.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20road%20Rang%20De%20is%20traversing%2C%20Ram%20says%20it%20is%20a%20long%20one.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20to%20impact%20a%20million%20social%20investors%20and%20households%20that%20the%20investment%20is%20helping.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Shinde%20who%20now%20watches%20with%20happiness%20as%20his%20friend%20drives%20an%20e-rickshaw%2C%20feels%20proud.%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20happy%20I%20could%20do%20my%20bit%20for%20the%20locals%20of%20Matheran%2C%20who%20take%20great%20pride%20in%20their%20work.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EInvest%20in%20an%20e-rickshaw%20and%20help%20hand%20rickshaw%20pullers%20today!%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frangde.in%2Ffund%2Fmatheranerickshawfund%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInvest%20Now%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EUnable%20to%20view%20the%20above%20button%3F%20%3Ca%20href%3D%