radise%20of%20a%20place%2C%20the%20little%20girl%20does%20not%20need%20to%20wander%20much%20to%20find%20her%20mother.%20She%20is%20bound%20to%20be%20in%20her%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F298110%2Fharyana-engineer-revives-traditional-pottery-earns-lakhs-by-selling-clay-utensils%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epottery%20studio%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20sits%20beside%20the%20towering%20tamarind%20tree.%20Right%20enough%2C%20Kavita%20is%20moulding%20wet%20clay%20into%20utensils%20and%20delicate%20urns%20that%20she%20neatly%20arranges%20along%20the%20studio%E2%80%99s%20many%20shelves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDevaki%20watches%20on%20intently%2C%20admiring%20the%20alchemy%20of%20clay%20being%20given%20life%20through%20these%20items.%20Then%2C%20once%20she%20is%20sure%20she%20isn%E2%80%99t%20interrupting%20the%20process%2C%20she%20begins%20to%20chat.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20my%20favourite%20part%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20%E2%80%9CAnother%20favourite%20part%20of%20my%20day%20is%20playing%20with%20my%20friend%20Deep.%E2%80%9D%20As%20Kavita%20explains%2C%20Deep%20is%20the%20caretaker%E2%80%99s%20son%20who%20has%20grown%20up%20alongside%20Devaki%20on%20the%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20pretend%20play%2C%20swing%2C%20do%20gymnastics%2C%20run%2C%20skateboard%2C%E2%80%9D%20Devaki%20continues%2C%20thoughtfully%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20always%20looking%20out%20for%20the%20animals%20and%20birds.%20Sometimes%20Deep%20and%20I%20act%20as%20the%20animal%20rescue%20team.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%E2%80%99d%20agree%20that%20Devaki%20is%20a%20lucky%20girl.%20Not%20many%20are%20fortunate%20to%20grow%20up%20away%20from%20the%20chokehold%20of%20technology%20but%20instead%20surrounded%20by%20paddy%20fields%2C%20flower%20beds%2C%20and%20streams.%20In%202020%2C%20when%20Kavita%20and%20Manoj%20decided%20to%20take%20the%20plunge%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%