g%20interest%20to%20her%20husband%E2%80%99s%20home%20along%20with%20her%20clothes%20and%20jewellery!%20%E2%80%9CMy%20husband%E2%80%99s%20place%20did%20not%20have%20many%20plants%20except%20bananas%20and%20drumsticks.%20I%20started%20planting%20flowering%20plants%20like%20marigolds%20and%20bougainvillaea%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%2C%20Jayanti%20visited%20an%20offline%20exhibition%20where%20she%20was%20introduced%20to%20the%20concept%20of%20grafting.%20%E2%80%9CI%20saw%20trees%20like%20mangoes%2C%20oranges%2C%20and%20chikoos%20were%20grown%20in%20a%20pot!%20Before%20this%2C%20I%20had%20only%20seen%20these%20trees%20on%20large%20farms.%20Unlike%20them%2C%20these%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F338660%2Fhow-to-grow-fruits-on-terrace-gardening-tips-visakhapatnam-woman-wins-award%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efruit%20trees%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewere%20just%205%20to%208%20feet%20in%20height%2C%20but%20they%20were%20yielding%20fruits.%20I%20was%20eager%20to%20grow%20such%20fruit%20trees%20at%20my%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJayanti%E2%80%99s%20quest%20led%20her%20to%20create%20a%20mini%20jungle%20on%20her%20terrace%20and%20in%20her%20house.%20Along%20with%20seasonal%20vegetables%20like%20brinjals%2C%20cucumber%2C%20okra%2C%20spinach%2C%20tomatoes%2C%20radish%2C%20and%20more%2C%20she%20cultivates%2017%20kinds%20of%20fruit%20trees%20%E2%80%94%20including%20guavas%2C%20pomegranates%2C%20oranges%2C%20cherries%2C%20star%20fruit%2C%20white%20jamun%2C%20mulberries%2C%20apple%20bear%2C%20water%20apple%2C%20mangoes%2C%20and%20chikoos%20on%20her%20terrace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20all%2C%20I%20grow%20flowers%2C%20fruits%2C%20and%20vegetables%20in%20my%20house%20spread%20across%20a%20total%20area%20of%20about%201%2C500%20square%20feet%20including%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F30